1
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:42,060
=Twin Fire Dawn=

2
00:00:42,100 --> 00:00:45,060
=Episode 11=

3
00:00:45,900 --> 00:00:50,100
(Ten days later)

4
00:01:23,700 --> 00:01:25,580
Your wound has only just healed.

5
00:01:25,660 --> 00:01:27,100
You need to get more rest lately.

6
00:01:28,900 --> 00:01:30,020
I'm fine.

7
00:01:30,340 --> 00:01:31,460
I'm not that fragile.

8
00:01:32,860 --> 00:01:34,620
Come back early tonight.

9
00:01:34,700 --> 00:01:36,540
I'm planning
to make roast chicken for you.

10
00:01:38,180 --> 00:01:39,700
How did you know

11
00:01:40,300 --> 00:01:41,540
I like roast chicken?

12
00:01:43,860 --> 00:01:44,460
Oh.

13
00:01:44,900 --> 00:01:47,500
I only made it because I like it myself.

14
00:01:57,740 --> 00:01:59,580
I'll prepare a gift for you too.

15
00:02:07,860 --> 00:02:10,420
I'll prepare a gift for you too.

16
00:02:13,300 --> 00:02:14,420
Shaoyuan.

17
00:02:14,500 --> 00:02:16,139
You're really lucky.

18
00:02:16,140 --> 00:02:18,220
Do you know how hard

19
00:02:18,820 --> 00:02:20,899
Miss Xue has been taking care
of you these past few days?

20
00:02:20,900 --> 00:02:22,460
She's injured herself,

21
00:02:22,540 --> 00:02:24,060
yet she still put you first.

22
00:02:24,700 --> 00:02:26,100
If I were you,

23
00:02:26,220 --> 00:02:28,579
I'd completely forget about Miss Zhuang.

24
00:02:28,580 --> 00:02:31,300
After all, she's been gone for so long.

25
00:02:35,420 --> 00:02:36,740
Pretend I never said anything.

26
00:02:38,260 --> 00:02:39,540
What if I told you

27
00:02:40,580 --> 00:02:42,140
they're the same person?

28
00:02:43,020 --> 00:02:44,340
The same person?

29
00:02:45,540 --> 00:02:47,019
So when you said before

30
00:02:47,020 --> 00:02:49,380
their voices
and appearances were alike...

31
00:02:50,020 --> 00:02:51,220
Could it be...

32
00:02:52,700 --> 00:02:54,460
Then has she recognized you?

33
00:02:57,580 --> 00:02:59,140
She thinks I'm Gu Nianchi.

34
00:03:01,340 --> 00:03:03,140
Once I help her seek justice,

35
00:03:04,500 --> 00:03:06,300
it won't be too late
to tell her the truth.

36
00:03:08,100 --> 00:03:08,980
By the way,

37
00:03:09,620 --> 00:03:10,940
have you found Lily yet?

38
00:03:12,020 --> 00:03:14,340
We've searched everywhere
and still haven't found her.

39
00:03:14,700 --> 00:03:16,940
No one knows
if she already escaped Yancheng.

40
00:03:17,380 --> 00:03:18,420
Keep looking.

41
00:03:19,900 --> 00:03:21,660
After what she did,

42
00:03:22,140 --> 00:03:24,300
she has to pay the price herself.

43
00:03:24,340 --> 00:03:25,460
Yes.

44
00:03:27,020 --> 00:03:27,940
Let's go.

45
00:03:28,660 --> 00:03:30,059
Come somewhere with me.

46
00:03:30,060 --> 00:03:31,140
Where?

47
00:03:33,660 --> 00:03:35,140
You'll find out when we get there.

48
00:03:40,820 --> 00:03:42,780
The flowers at this shop
are so fresh today.

49
00:03:43,460 --> 00:03:45,619
But I think pink might look nicer.

50
00:03:45,620 --> 00:03:46,699
Red looks nice.

51
00:03:46,700 --> 00:03:48,179
Red looks nice.

52
00:03:48,180 --> 00:03:49,500
Wouldn't that be a little plain?

53
00:03:49,580 --> 00:03:50,579
Maybe add a bit of pink

54
00:03:50,580 --> 00:03:52,259
or white

55
00:03:52,260 --> 00:03:53,380
to brighten it up.

56
00:03:53,580 --> 00:03:54,379
Stop overthinking it.

57
00:03:54,380 --> 00:03:56,640
- Your wife will definitely love it.
- You really think so?

58
00:03:56,640 --> 00:03:57,620
She'll definitely love it.

59
00:03:59,620 --> 00:04:01,200
Maybe we should go back
and take another look.

60
00:04:01,200 --> 00:04:02,180
Come on, Shaoyuan.

61
00:04:02,740 --> 00:04:04,740
(Lao Fengxiang Jewelry Store)
Make way.

62
00:04:24,500 --> 00:04:25,460
Are you alright?

63
00:04:26,780 --> 00:04:27,900
Thank you.

64
00:04:32,500 --> 00:04:34,340
Commander, you're here.

65
00:04:38,420 --> 00:04:40,660
So that's the Commander?

66
00:04:42,540 --> 00:04:43,620
Commander.

67
00:04:43,660 --> 00:04:44,900
Have you eaten today?

68
00:04:45,100 --> 00:04:46,580
No.

69
00:04:50,140 --> 00:04:51,420
I'm giving you money.

70
00:04:52,420 --> 00:04:53,340
Here.

71
00:04:53,820 --> 00:04:55,060
One coin each.

72
00:04:55,780 --> 00:04:57,020
Thank you, Commander.

73
00:04:59,140 --> 00:05:00,380
Your hair's gotten longer.

74
00:05:01,820 --> 00:05:03,060
Thank you, Commander.

75
00:05:13,860 --> 00:05:14,740
Commander.

76
00:05:24,220 --> 00:05:25,780
Commander.

77
00:05:27,820 --> 00:05:29,260
When did you get back?

78
00:05:30,460 --> 00:05:31,980
The roast chicken is ready.

79
00:05:32,060 --> 00:05:33,220
Come downstairs and eat.

80
00:05:44,900 --> 00:05:46,500
I don't want that.

81
00:05:48,700 --> 00:05:50,180
I want you.

82
00:05:50,820 --> 00:05:51,540
Commander.

83
00:05:52,260 --> 00:05:53,660
I'm not feeling very well today.

84
00:05:54,140 --> 00:05:55,260
Maybe next time.

85
00:05:56,660 --> 00:05:57,940
Next time?

86
00:05:59,580 --> 00:06:01,540
You're my wife.

87
00:06:02,420 --> 00:06:04,500
If I want you,

88
00:06:05,100 --> 00:06:06,820
I'll have you whenever I please.

89
00:06:07,060 --> 00:06:08,260
Let go of me!

90
00:06:08,420 --> 00:06:09,700
Let go!

91
00:06:10,100 --> 00:06:11,620
Let go!

92
00:06:23,620 --> 00:06:24,740
Still so fiery.

93
00:06:28,860 --> 00:06:30,740
Sooner or later, you'll be mine.

94
00:06:44,580 --> 00:06:45,700
Darling.

95
00:06:45,980 --> 00:06:47,300
You're back.

96
00:06:54,100 --> 00:06:55,540
Why are you here?

97
00:06:55,780 --> 00:06:57,860
I came to talk to my dear brother.

98
00:06:58,100 --> 00:06:59,060
Perfect timing.

99
00:07:00,060 --> 00:07:01,780
I have something
to discuss with you too.

100
00:07:16,020 --> 00:07:17,420
What is it? Go ahead.

101
00:07:19,380 --> 00:07:21,420
You've been sick for quite a while now.

102
00:07:21,460 --> 00:07:22,619
As your brother,

103
00:07:22,620 --> 00:07:24,740
I haven't properly checked in on you.

104
00:07:25,580 --> 00:07:26,739
I just wanted to see

105
00:07:26,740 --> 00:07:28,940
how well your sister-in-law
has been taking care of you.

106
00:07:29,260 --> 00:07:30,100
What a coincidence.

107
00:07:30,180 --> 00:07:32,660
I was about to say the same thing.

108
00:07:33,380 --> 00:07:34,500
Oh?

109
00:07:34,860 --> 00:07:38,180
From today onward, she belongs to me.

110
00:07:41,300 --> 00:07:42,540
Didn't you say before,

111
00:07:43,220 --> 00:07:45,019
you weren't interested in her?

112
00:07:45,020 --> 00:07:46,220
That was before.

113
00:07:46,660 --> 00:07:48,180
Now that I've saved her,

114
00:07:48,460 --> 00:07:50,180
she's mine.

115
00:07:54,260 --> 00:07:55,379
You risked your life

116
00:07:55,380 --> 00:07:57,060
to save my wife.

117
00:07:57,860 --> 00:07:58,900
With that...

118
00:07:59,180 --> 00:08:01,740
As your older brother,
I really should thank you properly.

119
00:08:03,060 --> 00:08:05,460
Looks like I haven't
done enough as your brother.

120
00:08:05,740 --> 00:08:06,740
Another day,

121
00:08:07,140 --> 00:08:09,180
I'll punish myself with three drinks

122
00:08:09,420 --> 00:08:11,380
and thank you properly.

123
00:08:11,740 --> 00:08:12,860
No need.

124
00:08:14,100 --> 00:08:15,460
I only want her.

125
00:08:21,860 --> 00:08:23,620
Then let's make a bet.

126
00:08:24,140 --> 00:08:26,220
We'll see who she chooses.

127
00:08:27,580 --> 00:08:28,860
I'm telling you,

128
00:08:29,580 --> 00:08:32,260
she belongs to me alone.

129
00:08:37,300 --> 00:08:38,420
Fine.

130
00:08:39,500 --> 00:08:41,340
Since you like her that much,

131
00:08:42,380 --> 00:08:43,860
you can have her.

132
00:08:45,180 --> 00:08:46,300
Alright.

133
00:08:46,460 --> 00:08:47,740
Let's talk business.

134
00:08:48,140 --> 00:08:49,620
Tomorrow, stay hidden.

135
00:08:50,780 --> 00:08:51,900
Don't show yourself.

136
00:08:52,740 --> 00:08:54,740
What could possibly require you
to appear in person?

137
00:08:56,200 --> 00:08:59,940
Tomorrow, the Commander's Residence
is hosting the annual Fragrance Gala.

138
00:09:00,660 --> 00:09:02,220
You won't be able to handle it.

139
00:09:04,900 --> 00:09:06,920
You even needed me to stand in
for your wedding night.

140
00:09:06,940 --> 00:09:08,260
Could a Fragrance Gala

141
00:09:08,900 --> 00:09:10,580
really matter more
than your own wedding?

142
00:09:11,780 --> 00:09:13,820
Isn't Li Shuche coming tomorrow?

143
00:09:13,980 --> 00:09:14,980
I know.

144
00:09:15,140 --> 00:09:16,740
You don't like him.

145
00:09:17,820 --> 00:09:18,540
That's true.

146
00:09:19,020 --> 00:09:20,380
I don't want to see him.

147
00:09:23,380 --> 00:09:24,500
The flowers look nice.

148
00:09:48,800 --> 00:09:50,700
How did he suddenly
become like a different person?

149
00:10:11,740 --> 00:10:14,260
Xue Wan, I'm back.

150
00:10:14,660 --> 00:10:16,860
Go away. I don't want to see you.

151
00:10:19,060 --> 00:10:19,980
No...

152
00:10:20,940 --> 00:10:21,820
Xue Wan.

153
00:10:22,580 --> 00:10:23,859
What happened?

154
00:10:23,860 --> 00:10:25,220
Open the door, Xue Wan.

155
00:10:29,540 --> 00:10:30,819
Didn't you hear me talking to you?

156
00:10:30,820 --> 00:10:32,260
I don't want to see you.

157
00:10:38,260 --> 00:10:39,220
Xue Wan.

158
00:10:39,780 --> 00:10:41,140
Open the door, Xue Wan.

159
00:10:41,300 --> 00:10:42,340
Get lost!

160
00:10:46,460 --> 00:10:47,660
(Gu Nianchi...)

161
00:10:48,380 --> 00:10:50,020
(What exactly did you do?)

162
00:11:01,500 --> 00:11:03,060
You've worked hard these past few days.

163
00:11:03,580 --> 00:11:06,980
Tomorrow's Fragrance Gala
won't require your help anymore.

164
00:11:10,180 --> 00:11:11,900
I bought concert tickets for you.

165
00:11:12,380 --> 00:11:14,100
Tomorrow, go relax and enjoy yourself.

166
00:11:15,220 --> 00:11:16,940
The Fragrance Gala...

167
00:11:19,460 --> 00:11:21,100
I'll leave the tickets by the door.

168
00:11:21,500 --> 00:11:23,140
Tomorrow, I'll
have someone escort you there.

169
00:11:25,280 --> 00:11:30,670
♪Love quietly hides within the wind♪

170
00:11:31,210 --> 00:11:35,779
♪Falling into your smile before my eyes♪

171
00:11:35,780 --> 00:11:36,980
(Yunqiu...)

172
00:11:37,700 --> 00:11:39,259
(I became his stand in)

173
00:11:39,260 --> 00:11:41,460
(all to wait
for tomorrow's Fragrance Gala.)

174
00:11:42,340 --> 00:11:44,280
(As long as everything
goes smoothly tomorrow...)

175
00:11:45,300 --> 00:11:46,860
(we'll finally be reunited.)

176
00:11:48,790 --> 00:11:54,600
♪Love is so strange,
the way it entangles me♪

177
00:11:56,980 --> 00:12:01,670
♪How can broken love ever go on?♪

178
00:12:02,980 --> 00:12:08,300
♪How much hope must fade into despair?♪

179
00:12:08,800 --> 00:12:12,380
♪In the blink of an eye,
everything falls apart♪

180
00:12:12,720 --> 00:12:15,730
♪Bound by the fate we cannot escape♪

181
00:12:15,900 --> 00:12:21,020
♪You and I caught in
this tangled love and hate♪

182
00:12:22,140 --> 00:12:27,330
♪Fragile hearts can hardly bear goodbye♪

183
00:12:28,390 --> 00:12:33,990
♪How many times
must pain cut deep before we wake?♪

184
00:12:34,530 --> 00:12:37,910
♪I once gave myself
to you so completely♪

185
00:12:38,160 --> 00:12:41,109
♪Still holding on to that heart♪

186
00:12:41,110 --> 00:12:46,249
♪Only to suffer your fatal blow♪

187
00:12:46,250 --> 00:12:50,569
♪How desperately
I long to hold you close♪

188
00:12:50,570 --> 00:12:53,149
♪Yet I approach you with such caution♪

189
00:12:53,150 --> 00:12:55,429
♪How could a stand in ever have♪

190
00:12:55,430 --> 00:12:58,979
♪The right to be loved by you?♪

191
00:12:58,980 --> 00:13:03,509
♪If love is nothing
more than endless schemes♪

192
00:13:03,510 --> 00:13:06,040
♪Used and abandoned in the end♪

193
00:13:06,180 --> 00:13:08,129
♪Still I walk into♪

194
00:13:08,130 --> 00:13:11,729
♪The trap you set without regret♪

195
00:13:11,730 --> 00:13:15,779
♪How desperately
I long to hold you close♪

196
00:13:15,780 --> 00:13:18,359
♪Yet keep it buried deep inside♪

197
00:13:18,360 --> 00:13:20,519
♪A stand in can never cross♪

198
00:13:20,520 --> 00:13:23,959
♪The shortest distance between us♪

199
00:13:23,960 --> 00:13:28,930
♪If love can
make someone lose themselves♪

200
00:13:29,090 --> 00:13:33,760
♪Then let me stay by your side♪

201
00:13:36,540 --> 00:13:38,109
♪A substitute♪

202
00:13:38,110 --> 00:13:43,110
♪Needs no reason♪

